00:05:22.115 --> 00:05:25.655
Because now every browser is kind of
patched as much as they can be patched for

89
00:05:25.655 --> 00:05:27.650
security reasons.

90
00:05:27.650 --> 00:05:31.770
And also it kind of automatically
without the user intervention

91
00:05:31.770 --> 00:05:36.310
